Yes and no.

[Your _existing_ item sets will still work in-game.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/230175788#h2q1) However the item set creator itself won't be available in the updated client. Currently, Riot has no plans for implementing the feature in the updated client stating that ["... only an incredibly tiny percentage of players ever used the feature."](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/client-update/article/4ac7a0bc-8847-40cd-8efb-aa5aa3a660f4)

